spec_data.Name: texlive-pdf-trans
spec_data.Description:
pdf-trans is a set of macros offering various transformations
of TeX boxes (based on plain and pdfeTeX primitives). It was
initially inspired by trans.tex, remade to work with pdfTeX.
spec_data.Signature: RSA/SHA256, Sun 06 Aug 2017 07:38:34 AM EDT, Key ID f55e7430f5282ee4
spec_data.Summary: A set of macros for various transformations of TeX boxes
